{"tid":623982,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"好彩香港仲有你","createTime":"2018-04-10T12:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T06:40:55.000Z","uid":50208,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"bd79768ab2649809c7aa79768e72e0b769c0bf9f","tid":623982,"uid":50208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:11:16.000Z","msg":"啱先撘13X個位朋友仔 <br />\n唔該曬你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到巴士先發現銀包得翻張500<br />\n個西又唔記得增值<br />\n仲頭痕緊周圍問人唱錢個陣<br />\n點知你突然行過黎<br />\n比左7蚊我<br />\n然後就頭也不回咁落車<br />\n我仲未反應到<br />\n車就開走左開埋右<br />\n連佢個樣都見唔到<br />\n唔知你係咪拍羞呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween香港好難得仲可以有好人<br />\n下次我會將呢7蚊還比其他有需要嘅人<br />\n希望你嘅好會感染埋比其他人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45603823545dad49a42e27dc99adb07b5eed1ef","tid":623982,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"還返7蚊俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8821eccf66c9730caa25fb6b843d41a1a4c937e","tid":623982,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:34:29.000Z","msg":"客咩氣"},{"pid":"537fb07b8588fcfef00f3870dfb2af36d494a60e","tid":623982,"uid":50208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d45603823545dad49a42e27dc99adb07b5eed1ef","tid":623982,"uid":29080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:32:40.000Z","msg":"還返7蚊俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"你走得咁快"},{"pid":"483d78842b88b6aa56ed05af6def2a7ac6719a7f","tid":623982,"uid":11506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:45:25.000Z","msg":"你個西點增值"},{"pid":"52b13d67d11cc277278287ef965eb3e31ed8d249","tid":623982,"uid":73897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"483d78842b88b6aa56ed05af6def2a7ac6719a7f","tid":623982,